     * Solutions
     * Compliance & Risk management

Utilizzate una soluzione di traduzione che rispetta la privacy dei dati & le
obbligazioni legali

Is Your Team Violating Data Compliance Laws by Using Online Translation
Tools?

   Globalization has brought companies new business opportunities that are
   often followed by a challenging landscape of rules, regulations and
   compliance pitfalls requiring various, complex content to be translated
   (due diligence reports, annual reports, audit memos, marketing
   materials, policies, contracts, technical risk reports...).
   Frost&Sullivan – Mcfee: The Hidden Truth Behind Shadow IT
   Frost&Sullivan – Mcfee: The Hidden Truth Behind Shadow IT
   CE Mark

   For companies looking to enter the European market, the CE Mark is a
   must. However, obtaining the CE Mark poses several translation
   challenges (products labels, instruction of use…). Also, companies
   dealing in financial services are facing new regulatory initiatives
   when implementing Governance, risk management and compliance (GRC)
   practices such as Sarbanes-Oxley and Basel III for banking and Solvency
   II for insurance.

   The use of non-approved applications, known as 'Shadow IT', leave your
   company vulnerable to losing confidential proprietary data, exposing
   customer information and violating uncontrolled data flow. For these
   reasons, translating online contravene with the existing standards and
   regulations.

   Whatever your industry, it is essential to provide employees with tools
   that respect your GRC policies and to communicate the risks of shadow
   IT and the benefits of using integrated tools.

Come possiamo aiutarvi?

   Centralizzazione del contenuto e del processo

   SYSTRAN delivers a fully integrated solution within your IT
   infrastructure providing you with a tailored and secured translation.

   Accurate Terminology & Compliance

Accurate Terminology & Compliance

   Whatever your industry, SYSTRAN integrates your specific terminology
   into our tools. All your multilingual materials are accurate in each
   context and in accordance with local, regional and global regulations.

Accurate Terminology & Compliance

   Data Security

Data Security

   Your data, financial and confidential information remains in your
   company.
   SYSTRAN’s solution can be implemented on-premises or hosted on a
   dedicated server.

Data Security

   Short Turnaround Times

Short Turnaround Times

   As timelines become tighter, SYSTRAN is a business-oriented solution
   that help you to maximize your productivity by translating a large
   volume of documents with a faster turnaround time.

Short Turnaround Times

   Total Cost of Ownership

Total Cost of Ownership

   SYSTRAN’s translation memory centralizes your translation processes
   while reducing translation costs. Once key compliance program documents
   are initially translated, you will only need to update your materials
   for subsequent translations.

Total Cost of Ownership

